-- Northam Platinum Says Two Miners Killed in an Accident at Zondereinde Mine
-- Alastair Reed
-- 2010-07-20T15:54:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-20/northam-platinum-says-two-miners-killed-in-an-accident-at-zondereinde-mine.html

          
          
             Northam Platinum Ltd. said two
workers were killed in an accident at its Zondereinde mine in
South Africa earlier today.  
          
          


  


        